rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Oh, fondant greetings to you!
We are glad to see you well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0030
rows.name:
Oh, we were lucky to land not far from here,
so we made it back under our own power.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0040
rows.name: Times like these, slow and steady bakes the cake![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0045
rows.name: Keep your goal in focus, and one may never fail![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0050
rows.name:
But come, let us stick a thumbtack in the celebrations.
The final stage still awaits us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0060
rows.name: Into the lion's gullet! As flies to wonton soup are we![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33540100_MSG0070
rows.name: ...Incidentally, we may need to further look into that last one.[ST:wait ]
